---
/**
 * Lifestyle — editorial two-column section.
 * Large image left with numbered caption, copy block right.
 */
---

<section class="lifestyle" data-reveal>
  <p class="lifestyle__label">The Lifestyle</p>

  <div class="lifestyle__grid">
    <div class="lifestyle__media">
      <div class="lifestyle__image">
        <img src="/images/lifestyle-neighbourhood.jpg" alt="Couple walking along the bay at golden hour, Edgewater neighbourhood" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="lifestyle__caption">
        <p class="lifestyle__caption-number">(6)</p>
        <p class="lifestyle__caption-text">A neighbourhood that hasn't lost its soul</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lifestyle__copy">
      <p>
        Kayak paddles on glass water before the city wakes. A Cubano at
        Enriqueta's before the heat hits. Margaret Pace Park at golden hour,
        where everyone ends up eventually.
      </p>
      <p>
        Five minutes from Wynwood's galleries, ten from the Design District,
        fifteen from the sand. But the reason people stay is the bay. Morning
        light that turns the water from navy to teal to gold in the time it
        takes to finish a coffee.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lifestyle__pair">
    <div class="lifestyle__pair-image">
      <img src="/images/lifestyle-yoga.jpg" alt="Morning yoga on a wooden terrace, aerial view" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="lifestyle__pair-image">
      <img src="/images/lifestyle-plunge.jpg" alt="Cold plunge pool in warm ambient light" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
